130763150d9c8f42a48968cd4b8c1f355bf5e71","tid":694143,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"老人政治，唔比位下一代上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3e147697037730352e68e1c813b7231c9a7ee6","tid":694143,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"有次開唔知咩會條友又係傻下傻下"},{"pid":"23964c779b6f201dbb6ecfda12f1e51a853f2ad3","tid":694143,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"白頭佬係咪同雪廠街一樣, 有把柄落咗係人手?"},{"pid":"83e37f8d7af73c92dda44a1244454929627be493","tid":694143,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"呢件白頭佬應該收左支那好處<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係有主席又唔做, 有自己個黨又搞到鬼咁亂"},{"pid":"3b40ece05579a83774726c9202ae3bfdba19c1b3","tid":694143,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:26:15.000Z","msg":"冇得撈政治綜援了。"},{"pid":"6a0f3e9c466b69e163badf3ad56aa4e312d58d36","tid":694143,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明做左十幾年政棍都相安無事，自從主席個件事之後醜聞一單接一單，睇黎主席件事真係搞到佢亂晒大龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢邊止十幾年呀，條友好似97前已經做緊啦"}]}